{"tid":1525571,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人連罷工都唔敢，就唔好再講咩抗爭啦","createTime":"2019-09-01T01:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:57:04.000Z","uid":259581,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c18df790af82f0ee57c834770ed43aad502d2c09","tid":1525571,"uid":259581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:33:40.000Z","msg":"罷工已經係最和平，最無危險嘅抗爭，如果咁都唔做，不如直接加入大灣區好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n無限期罷工，至少一兩星期，直至政府重組<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n罷工期間<br />\n唔shopping，只買生活必需品<br />\n唔出街食，只去良心小店，自己煮<br />\n唔去旅行，只去行山，踩單車<br />\n唔去睇戲，只睇書，睇netfilx<br />\n<br />\n之後好多大型藍絲機構，集團就會有倒閉潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n樓市股票將會大跌，回復到正常水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d470c1f77173ac25b2ce04ad6bf2a8ccdc541d","tid":1525571,"uid":242083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:34:08.000Z","msg":"831恐襲同721恐襲冇分別<br />\n我正式宣佈香港警察係有牌黑社會兼恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeYzNsiOy00o&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=b0f09441\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eYzNsiOy00o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/r2_c1Lc6MiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fr2_c1Lc6MiU&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b29Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=9328548f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/r2_c1Lc6MiU</a>"},{"pid":"50e18dda364841459855c0c0a49c9a254a48b95b","tid":1525571,"uid":278392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:34:29.000Z","msg":"今日跳閘被藍絲廢老足到 隔離冇人幫手 因為仲好早 冇乜人流 還唔到手 仲要將我一野拍落塊玻璃到<br />\n注意事項如下<br />\n跳閘最好唔好自己一個人 隔離冇人幫拖又有幾個藍絲捉住你 你幾大隻幾想還手都好都冇用<br />\n<br />\n仲有！好多人流傳填form ge時候填假地址就得係假<br />\n首先入到去 佢會要你身份證 呢個時候你可能會唔俾 但唔俾佢會直接報警<br />\n俾左身份證之後 其實你填咩假地址都冇用 要揾你實搵到<br />\n你可能會話 人地得鬼閒咁落力揾你咩<br />\n我可以答你 唔會 我即時問個個職員（佢似係我地陣營）佢地會直接將你個人資料上交法律部門（應該係黨鐵ge法務部）如果冇係限期之內交500罰款 係會將案件上交法庭<br />\n所以唔好再諗可以填假地址 要跳就揾幾個人一齊跳 唔好自己一個！"},{"pid":"4f0debfef79cadd8487dee4e36631c205158a9a3","tid":1525571,"uid":265498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:35:21.000Z","msg":"[901和你飛］作戰任務地點！！！職員爆料，一，二號檢查閘<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524355</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0fa445bc6fc3521b590da0c934600be7e43fc97a","tid":1525571,"uid":259581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T01:50:23.000Z","msg":"罷工啦"},{"pid":"2d1b1600c344be282621e037bfe96a2b3cc65d5f","tid":1525571,"uid":259581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T02:25:07.000Z","msg":"罷工！！！"},{"pid":"77fec5c7bc4c45881007225f6caf3be7b32ba81b","tid":1525571,"uid":140650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T03:10:35.000Z","msg":"9.2開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946c9997c687110c3fd304cb63b0af7aeb98bb6d","tid":1525571,"uid":259581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}